1. *Čujete* li me? (Do you hear me?)
2. *Čujete* li kako se deca igraju? (Do you hear how the children are playing?)
3. Oni su *čuli* da je ona izgubila posao. (They heard that she lost her job.)
4. Moramo *čuti* šta nam je rekao. (We have to hear what he told us.)
5. Nije *čuo* šta je rekao. (He didn't hear what he said.)
6. Ona *čuje* da je ona lepa. (She hears that she's beautiful.)